{"tid":1468440,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［反民意撚][反左膠]到底點解仲會咁介意民意","createTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T19:31:18.000Z","uid":26532,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"382c97d9def0cf390c95ee18b35a26c11c0862d8","tid":1468440,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:40:40.000Z","msg":"利申 : 反打First aids記者 反搞遊客 反無理暴力<br />\n<br />\n但我唔明，今日打公安同發生衝突都要比人屌係為乜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.成日有堆人衝出黎話做呢樣做果樣就會失民意<br />\n<br />\n唔好咁撚天真啦...要分黃藍一早分撚左啦 你打鳩差佬/打公安/唔比佢走就會冇哂支持冇哂民意?係黃底既點都會支持落去架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋民意真係有用? 就算呢一刻90%民意支持 政府根本唔會聽唔會有改變<br />\n<br />\n問心啦 你地口講不割席 但由頭到尾根本就因為怕人割席所以乜柒都唔敢做<br />\n<br />\n2. 個個開口埋口 以眼還眼 錫春袋 etc.<br />\n<br />\n上到場就左膠上身 甚至救人都唔敢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地諗返起狗咁撚樣對義士啦 仲要良心去對待班公安同狗?<br />\n<br />\n3.個個叫唔好捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n根本問題唔係捉鬼呢個行為身上 係今日無理暴力先咁姐<br />\n<br />\n你以為唔捉鬼咁前線點算 ? 到時痴根本任玩唔嬲<br />\n<br />\n不如諗下點樣忍下手好過直頭連鬼都唔捉啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有好多人今次真係當打杖咁上場<br />\n<br />\n得自已都覺.但我唔明點解而家打緊杖都可以咁理敵人既安危. 一陣又話驚激嬲共狗 一陣又怕美國唔支持 一陣又怕自已道德高地冇左<br />\n<br />\n你有道德就會贏到場革命?咪撚玩啦....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51052b81bef0ff28d8653345da5cbee05f5ce525","tid":1468440,"uid":117550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"(突發)航空公司   民航處  機管局講大話<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468306</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc29f5f11b38c0bba15fcda613d41618c7351f15","tid":1468440,"uid":173850,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:42:42.000Z","msg":"民意好重要 黃背心一無民意都即收皮"},{"pid":"99124870c30f7aa072202c524f2a8b3b607c0cf4","tid":1468440,"uid":196114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:43:17.000Z","msg":"講得非常好"},{"pid":"5cca16c9ec2787fb533c03d19f5b88a4fb65d075","tid":1468440,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:44:47.000Z","msg":"關於機場禁制令<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468334</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係怕民意，係怕外交"},{"pid":"89a141ede6600700d29e9cb408eb117bfbf9fced","tid":1468440,"uid":166567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:45:21.000Z","msg":"狗可打，不主動開波"},{"pid":"1c55a0a62edb28ad91ec2a5cc863e4fd57cbfc2b","tid":1468440,"uid":190700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9mGz9aP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9mGz9aP.jpg&h=cb4f2ed7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KQCGPaT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKQCGPaT.jpg&h=14cd11cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XdF1PaT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXdF1PaT.jpg&h=9a7cb9e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d275546a842de7f47b2a92abd6dca96ba16b123d","tid":1468440,"uid":258208,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:49:56.000Z","msg":"場運動延續到依家就係靠民意<br />\n前線示威者衝擊 背後有強大民意支持認同<br />\n自己圍威喂晨早玩完喇"},{"pid":"ab913e882905748dbb2ba4afbd36a3de4a759ec7","tid":1468440,"uid":274513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:50:51.000Z","msg":"無民意激嬲左大眾，黑警打死你都無人會幫你"},{"pid":"9f8944669ed251b7fa98e707ba28f40b8a097350","tid":1468440,"uid":26532,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:58:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2810d7e563a789b8b00878119cb084909b2a3e","tid":1468440,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"